    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, it's a lovely night for a cricket update, how's your team doing these days?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "We won an important match today! Our team is in the top 4 now. The batsmen did well, but the bowlers were a bit shaky."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Great job, winning feels amazing! The top 4 is a strong position. What part of the match felt most exciting for you?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The last over was super tense—we were chasing a high score, and the bowler took a wicket in the last ball. It felt like *chak de* moment! But we won by 2 runs."
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That was intense, winning by 2 runs is thrilling! I get why you said *chak de*, those moments feel huge. Did you cheer with anyone while watching?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I was with some friends at a small cricket café. We were shouting, clapping, and even danced a little when we won! It’s always better with others. Do you watch cricket, Maya?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re describing it so well, café, shouting, dancing, yes! That’s the spirit. I do watch cricket, love the energy. What team are you cheering for these days?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I support Mumbai Indians mostly—great mix of experienced and young players. But honestly, I enjoy watching any good match. Have you seen the new season?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Mumbai Indians are an exciting team, right, full of energy and talent. I get that, good matches are always fun to watch. What’s your favourite part of the game?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The power plays are my favorite—when the batsmen score really fast, or the bowlers take a wicket early. It sets the tone for the whole game. Though I also love the tension in the death overs. It’s like *adrenalin* kicks in! What about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it, power plays and death overs are the highlights for many. Adrenalin is definitely part of the fun! Do you follow any specific players?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I like Virat Kohli and Jasprit Bumrah the most—Kohli’s determination is inspiring, and Bumrah’s yorkers are *unbeatable*. I also follow some young players, like Rajasthan’s Sai Sudharsan. What about you, any favorite players?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Virat and Bumrah are solid choices, Kohli’s grit and Bumrah’s yorkers are iconic! Sai Sudharsan is rising fast, good eye there. Do you follow any international players too?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Not really, I mostly stick to the Indian league and team. But I do get updates about the Aussies and the West Indies sometimes. Their matches seem *very competitive*. Maybe I should watch more. Thanks for the suggestion!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re welcome, the Aussies and West Indies add great energy to the game, it’s easy to get hooked! When do you find time to watch matches these days?"
    }
